column6: Flavum is the old nomenclature for convictum.
May be notated "longinmanus" rather than "longimana" in taxonomist's notes
Virgatanytarsus is the old nomenclature for Caladomyia (Caladomiya is the North American genus previously ID'ed as Virgatanytarsus).
